18#include <string>
19
20namespace ZXing {
21
22enum class CharacterSet;
23class BitMatrix;
24
25namespace Aztec {
26
27class Writer
28{
29public:
30 Writer();
31
32 Writer& setMargin(int margin) {
33 _margin = margin;
34 return *this;
35 }
36
37 Writer& setEncoding(CharacterSet encoding) {
38 _encoding = encoding;
39 return *this;
40 }
41
42 Writer& setEccPercent(int percent) {
43 _eccPercent = percent;
44 return *this;
45 }
46
47 Writer& setLayers(int layers) {
48 _layers = layers;
49 return *this;
50 }
51
52 BitMatrix encode(const std::wstring& contents, int width, int height) const;
53
54private:
55 CharacterSet _encoding;
56 int _eccPercent;
57 int _layers;
58 int _margin = 0;
59};
60
61} // Aztec
62} // ZXing
